OUR MISSION

Venture Capital, the Wix way

At Wix Ventures, we’re more than investors. We empower bold entrepreneurs through strategic capital and guidance, global reach and unmatched expertise, helping early-stage companies go further, faster.

We’re always looking for extraordinary founders in the pre-seed and seed stages that are building innovative technologies, creative solutions and have disruptive business models that align with our core mission of shaping the future of the web. As a startup turned global leader, we know the ropes and are determined to help visionaries turn big ideas into thriving companies.
